         Aye, Dot stacking is mainly an end-game fix.  It won't do squat in exp groups and you won't see groups of tons of Necros doing more then they already are.  Dot stacking is just a nice way of letting multiple Necros cast their best dots on a mob without having to play around with seeing who will cast what and not fill up the icon buffer.  Anything above 3 or 4 Necros getting a dot a piece turns into Necros that just nuke or bring another class.</P><P>"Time is meaningless to one who lives forever."<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
