        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         DoTs are not Debuffs at all alike. VI can make scripts to differentiate between them; this is proven as Affliction items only affect DoTs and not Debuffs/Snare. Making DoT stacking would be difficult, but VI has done harder for less need. Do not attempt to draw analogies/comparisons, there is no other class that has their DPS/usefullness drop when there are more than 2 present, many classes increase.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
