         Can't say I have raided with more than 2 epic enchanters..... but they're abilities don't lie in damage at all so much helping others damage.</P><P>Now onto why DoT stacking should be done. Its not about being bored, its about contributing enough to be worth taking along. Lets take a couple times ago killing Gorenaire. There were 2 necros there. I cast Pyrocruor, it landed and I assume did the full 2k damage. Nothing else landed. So, 1 necro did 2k damage. This is easily outdone by a single wizzie nuke. But there were 2 necros there. The second one did zero. Had the been a dozen copies of us, the total damage would still be 2k. A dozen necros would be outdamaged by a single wizzie nuke, as the non skele nukes are far too rare to be obtainable. Necros can solo very well, but you can not do the high end game solo. Dot stacking is neccesary to make it worth having necros in the guild.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
